<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Email Subject</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset styles to ensure consistent rendering */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* Add styles to your email content */
        .email-content {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 2rem auto 0;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        a {
            color: #0088cc;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        span {
            font-weight: 100;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-content">
        <h1>New Quotation Request From Customer</h1>
        <p>Dear Admin,</p>
        <p>
            I hope this email finds you well.
            I am writing to inform you that we have received a new quotation request from a customer through our website.
            The details of the quotation request are as follows:
        </p>
        <p>
        <h4>Customer Name : <span>%username%</span> </h4>
        <h4>Customer Email : <span>%usermail%</span> </h4>
        <h4>Customer Phone Number : <span>%userphno%</span> </h4>
        <h4>Customer Address : <span>%useraddress%</span> </h4>
        </p>
        <!-- <h3>Product Details :- </h3> 
        <p>
