            <h4>Quantity : <span>100</span></h4>
            <h4>Bag Type : <span>Jute</span></h4>
            <h4>Bag Specifications : <span>company name and log</span></h4>
        </p> -->

        <p>Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter.
            Your expertise and professionalism in handling customer requests are greatly appreciated.
        </p>

        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>Starling bags.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>